Subject:      Butor blues version
 
Butor Blues
 
              (Paul Butorfield version)
 
 
From <snap> to <snap>             <snaps fingers into microphone>
I bend my ways, baby...
From squeal to squeal             <5-min. harmonica break>
I tree my tour...
 
                                  <30 min. Indian raga>
