***********************************
* The Kootenay School of Writing  *
* Vancouver B.C., Canada          *
* EVENTS FOR APRIL 1996           *
*                                 *
* email: ksw@wimsey.com           *
* www: http://www.wimsey.com/~ksw *
* 112 West Hastings               *
